quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  18,98,"Julqarnayni wi'i: "Ngoo heedo ko Yurmeende immornde ka Joomi am nde no heeda hakkunde Yaajuuja e Maajuuja e bonnugol ka leydi, ngo haЙ—a Й“e e Й—um, si waqtu mo Alla happi on fii yaltugol maЙ“Й“e ado dargol Darngal ngal arii O wattinay ngo feppondirngo e leydi ndin, Fodoore Alla nden fii feppindirgol ngo e leydi ndin e yaltugol Yaajuuja e Maajuuja laatike ko tabituЙ—um lurral alaa e mu'un"."
  18,99,"Men acca woЙ“Й“e e tagu ngun ka sakkitoode jamaanu ngun no ukkondira jillondira e woЙ“Й“e, alaadu ndun wuttee Men mooЙ“i tagu ngun kala maggu fii hasboore nden e njoЙ“de ndin."
  18,100,"Men fenГұinanay Jahannama yedduЙ“e Й“en fenГұinngol ngol aldaa e jiЙ“ayee fii yo Й“e seedo nge gite."
  18,101,"Men fenГұinana nge yedduЙ“e Й“en, Й“en laatinooЙ“e ko bumЙ“e e jantagol Alla ka aduna; sabu ko woni kon ka gite maЙ“Й“e e wirngallo haЙ—ayngo Й—um, Й“e laatii Й“e hattantaake nanugol Aayeeje Alla Й—en nanЙ—e jabugol."
  18,102,"Enee Й“en yedduЙ“e Alla sikku Й“e waЙ—ay jeyaaЙ“e Am Й“en immorde e Malaa'ikaaЙ“e e NulaaЙ“e e Seytanuuji reweteeЙ“e gaanin Am?! Menen Men heblanii Jahannama fii yedduЙ“e Й“en galle fii werde maЙ“Й“e."
  18,103,"Maaku -an NulaaЙ—o-: "Taw si men humpitay on -ko onon yo yimЙ“e- Й“urЙ—o mawnude yimЙ“e Й“en hayrere ka golle makko?"
  18,104,"ЖҒen yi'ayЙ“e Г‘alnde Darngal wonnde golle maЙ“Й“e Й—e Й“e wonnoo gollude Й—en ka aduna Й—e yeebike, hari kamЙ“e hiЙ“e sikka hiЙ“e moЖҙЖҙinnde ka golle maЙ“Й“e,Й—um non no lunndii goonga kan."
  18,105,"ЖҒen, ko kamЙ“e woni yedduЙ“e Й“en Aayeeje Joomi maЙ“Й“e tinndinЙ—e e ngootimbaaku, Й“e yeddi kadi hawrugol e Makko, golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en boniri sabu yeddugol maЙ“Й“e Й—um, laatanoytaako Й“e Г‘alnde Darngal geЙ“al ka Alla."
  18,106,"Ndin joЙ“di maranaandi Й“e ko Jahannama; sabu yeddugol maЙ“Й“e Alla, e jogitagol maЙ“Й“e Aayeeje Am jippinaaЙ—e Й—en e NulaaЙ“e Am Й“en jalnori."
  18,107,"Pellet, Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e Alla Й“e golli golle moЖҙЖҙe Й—en laatanoyto Й“e ka Й“uri toowude e Aljannaaji Й—in werde sabu teddinngol Й“e."
  18,108,"Ko ГұiiЙ“ooЙ“e nder ton poomaa, Й“e Й—aЙ“Й“ataa gaayi makko waЙ—titugol; sabu kanko njoЙ“di Й“adotaako mo."
  18,109,"Maaku -an NulaaЙ—o-: "Pellet, Daaluyeeji Joomi am Й—in ko Й—uuЙ—uЙ—i, sinno maayo ngon laatanino Й—i ndawa ka winndireeЙ—i diyam maayo ngo lannayno ko adii Daaluyeeji Makko Й—in lannude Senaande wonanii Mo, sinno en addiino kadi maaje goo, Й—en kadi lannayno"."
  18,110,"Maaku: -an NulaaЙ—o-: "Min dey, ko mi Й“anndinke yeru mo'on, no wahayinaa e am wonnde Rewetee- Й—o mon On ka Goonga ko O RerweteeЙ—o gooto kafidaaЙ—o(denndadiijo) alaanaa Mo, ko Kanko woni Alla, kala tawЙ—o no huli hawroydi e Joomi mu'un yo o gollu golle hawrondirЙ—e e Sari'a Makko on, ko o laЙ“Й“inanЙ—o Й—e Joomi makko, wata o kafidu e Dewal Joomi makko hay e gooto"."